{"tid":1571761,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【召集Deadline fighter 】廣東話要你救，要埋你啲fd救","createTime":"2019-09-15T13:49:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T15:46:52.000Z","uid":92277,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"b924065520bdd6772ca0b1b5d2cccd10bab7e0ab","tid":1571761,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T13:49:12.000Z","msg":"*我抄隔黎post既，因為太重要！<br />\n<br />\n中文科取消聆聽,說話嘅諮詢文件。應該係想幫內地生爭學位, 同埋淡化甚至消滅廣東話!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/about-edb/press/consultation/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edb.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fabout-edb%2Fpress%2Fconsultation%2F&d=02TnLe2cOfQrY9jdqtoXeQ2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=4c9fba23\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/about-edb/press/consultation/</a><br />\n<br />\n如果唔同意，請於二零一九年九月十六日（星期一）或之前，以郵寄、<br />\n電郵或傳真方式把書面意見交予專責小組秘書處：<br />\n郵寄地址： 香港灣仔<br />\n皇后大道東 213 號<br />\n胡忠大廈 13 樓 1301 室<br />\n學校課程檢討專責小組秘書處<br />\n電郵： taskforce_cur@edb.gov.hk<br />\n傳真號碼： (852) 2573 5299」<br />\n<br />\n_________________________________<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">Template在此👇，標題請自行撰寫</span></span><br />\n<br />\n致專責小組成員：<br />\n<br />\n本人為香港市民，有聞 貴組於6月28日文件中提出刪去文憑試聆聽及說話考卷，本人堅表強烈反對，原因如下：<br />\n<br />\n一，掌握母語不等於能以母語表達，說話要言之有物、出口成文，除了要豐富的詞彙，亦要有清晰的表達方式，說話卷的核心價值在於檢視學生在日常用語之外，能否有效建構論點展開討論，而廢除後則無地方訓練學生這頂基本能力。<br />\n<br />\n二，掌握母語不等於能理解別人話語內容，聆聽別人的說話可以訓練學生將對話精煉的能力，亦即是捕捉重點的能力，假如廢除，恐怕學生會失去一個練習的平台，無法與人有效溝通。<br />\n<br />\n三，以語言系公開試ielts雅思為例，考核學生英語水平以讀聽寫說四考卷，尤其是以說話難度最高，一向是該考試衡量英語高水平者的好標準，如今 貴組研廢除聆、說二卷，猶如自斷一臂。<br />\n<br />\n綜合以上及眾多學者之言，冀 貴組於此項教育改革方向予於重新考慮。<br />\n<br />\n一名香港市民<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wpGhiqO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwpGhiqO.jpg&h=f493d0b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">腥完share埋比fd, 再留言話Done! </span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nShared From fb"},{"pid":"ed45a71965046c5b101f182eb217094753169ebf","tid":1571761,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T13:50:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3fc3d406e84a058143c82ea0a7b0aae02cc0d061","tid":1571761,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T13:50:14.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"63cdc3080560f35f35b2633810250dcb655821c4","tid":1571761,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T13:50:33.000Z","msg":"福建幫打得好，但都要救廣東話"},{"pid":"b9c9d5329f423771d4cf8daf594674f59d047fb5","tid":1571761,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T13:50:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8c090443bde6aa22a933d3c377bdde201ce45134","tid":1571761,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T13:50:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7bd36e600f0dfd5b07f7ae9ec1adf495abee318c","tid":1571761,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T13:51:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fc96859b38b098eb788c17b6ad9e15abe33aa7ee","tid":1571761,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T13:51:41.000Z","msg":"屌救廣東話呀"},{"pid":"7decf18f9370fc5952dc8bd423af3db3ed85dd8e","tid":1571761,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T13:52:31.000Z","msg":"救呀"},{"pid":"43c2da40d4041e0c936e1c31370f139f048eef1c","tid":1571761,"uid":305725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T13:52:37.000Z","msg":"Done and shared"},{"pid":"c65fbb5316b2cbc65c89a231eda501313556c03a","tid":1571761,"uid":92277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T13:52:41.000Z","msg":"救呀屌你個閪"},{"pid":"fd1ca39f1d53ca1b4c7818cee1824e8424ba452b","tid":1571761,"uid":177853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T13:57:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ee3bae4a7b9fa33351756cad63b83ef6e90bb637","tid":1571761,